Christi Shepherd and her brother Robert died from carbon monoxide poisoning during a holiday in Corfu in October 2006 . 
  Father Neil Shepherd and his girlfriend Ruth Beatson were also almost killed by the fumes . 
  The family were staying at the four-star Corcyra Beach Hotel in the Greek island . 
  Christi and Bobby were overcome by fumes from a faulty boiler in the outhouse . 
  Their mother Sharon Wood was at the inquest into their deaths . 
  Father and girlfriend were also in a coma when they were found . 
 